+## Summary
+Updated server tests for the current JSON-RPC behavior: invalid batch entries are preserved as per-item error responses, local memory client snapshots now reflect the current chain state, and invalid-method tests no longer depend on forked remote transport behavior. Replaced network-bound `supertest` execution in server specs with a direct in-package request-listener test client so the suite validates handler behavior without binding a port.
+
+## Tests passing
+all
+
+## Tests still failing
+0
+
