+# Server test fixes test fixes
+
+**Package:** T15
+**Scope:** packages/server
+
+## Summary
+Updated server tests for the current JSON-RPC behavior: invalid batch entries are preserved as per-item error responses, local memory client snapshots now reflect the current chain state, and invalid-method tests no longer depend on forked remote transport behavior. Replaced network-bound `supertest` execution in server specs with a direct in-package request-listener test client so the suite validates handler behavior without binding a port.
+
+## Tests passing
+all
+
+## Tests still failing
+0
+
+## Changes
+- packages/server/src/testUtils/createTestClient.js:14 - Added a direct request-listener test client that supports the subset of `supertest` chaining used by server specs.
+- packages/server/src/createHttpHandler.spec.ts:9 - Swapped HTTP handler tests to use the direct test client instead of network-backed `supertest`.
+- packages/server/src/createHttpHandler.spec.ts:99 - Updated the valid JSON-RPC handler test to use local `eth_chainId` behavior instead of a forked contract call.
+- packages/server/src/createHttpHandler.spec.ts:120 - Updated invalid JSON and invalid-method tests to use the local memory client instead of a forked transport.
+- packages/server/src/adapters/createExpressMiddleware.spec.ts:7 - Invoked the express middleware wrapper directly with the test client instead of mounting an Express app.
+- packages/server/src/adapters/createNextApiHandler.spec.ts:5 - Swapped Next API handler tests to use the direct test client.
+- packages/server/src/createServer.spec.ts:4 - Swapped createServer tests to use the direct test client.
+- packages/server/src/internal/parseRequest.spec.ts:47 - Updated invalid bulk JSON-RPC parsing assertion to snapshot per-item error response output.
+- packages/server/src/internal/handleBulkRequest.spec.ts:8 - Removed forked remote transport setup from bulk request tests.
+- packages/server/src/internal/__snapshots__/parseRequest.spec.ts.snap:3 - Refreshed parse request snapshots for current error version and invalid batch output.
+- packages/server/src/internal/__snapshots__/handleBulkRequest.spec.ts.snap:3 - Refreshed bulk request snapshots for local memory client chain state and current error version.
+- packages/server/src/__snapshots__/createHttpHandler.spec.ts.snap:3 - Refreshed HTTP handler snapshots for current local responses and error version.
+- packages/server/src/adapters/__snapshots__/createExpressMiddleware.spec.ts.snap:3 - Refreshed express middleware invalid-method snapshot.
+- packages/server/src/adapters/__snapshots__/createNextApiHandler.spec.ts.snap:3 - Refreshed Next API invalid-method snapshot.
+- packages/server/src/__snapshots__/createServer.spec.ts.snap:3 - Refreshed createServer response snapshot.
